Board of Directors
About Magal / 

				Quickly Navigate: Home Page / 
			







About Magal
Company Overview
Executive Management
Board of Directors
International Standards
Corporate Governance 



Gillon Beck
Chairman of the Board from October 2014. Mr. Beck is a Senior partner in FIMI since 2003. 
Mr. Beck is the Chairman and Director of several other companies related to FIMI.
For more information please visit http://www.fimi.co.il/fimi-overview/management-team

Barry Stiefel 
was appointed by our Board of Directors in November 2008. Mr. Stiefel served as a Director of a UK subsidiary from 1986 to 1990. Since 2001, Mr. Stiefel has served as a consultant for a variety of companies. 
Mr. Stiefel holds a B.Sc degree in Mathematics and Chemistry and a B.A. degree in Accounting, both from the University of Witwatersrand in South Africa. 

Moshe Tsabari
Joined Magal's board as an external director in October 2014. Mr. Tsabari is a senior partner of “GME Trust” company and the founder of the ‘International institute for Researching the Arab World’. 
Mr. Tsabari served for 25 years in the Israeli military attending the rank of a brigadier serving as the Head of Operations. Mr. Tsabari holds three degrees from the Israel Institute of Technology: Bachelor's degree in geodetic engineering, a master's degree in Industrial Engineering, PhD in science. Graduate of the prestigious program for managers, Wharton's AMP.

Avraham Bigger
Joined Magal's board as an external director in October 2014. Mr. Bigger is the owner and director of Bigger Investment Ltd. and served as a member of the board of directors in leading banks, industries and communication companies.

Ron Ben-Haim
Joined Magal's board of directors in October 2014. Mr. Ben-Haim is Partner in FIMI since 2006. Mr. Ben-Haim is a Director of several other companies related to FIMI.
For more information please visit http://www.fimi.co.il/fimi-overview/management-team

Liza Singer
Became a Board member of Magal Security Systems as of June 30, 2010. 
Ms. Singer has been an owner’s representative for the Lewis Trust Group, in Cyprus, since 2003. 
Ms. Singer holds a Bachelor of Accounting degree and Bachelor of Law degree from Tel-Aviv University and an MBA from the Leon Recanati School of Business Administration in Israel.

Jacob Berman
Joined Magal's Board of Directors in 2003.Mr. Berman is the president of JB Advisors, an advisory ferm in New-York and the Chairman of the Board of Directors of Israel Discount Bank of New York.
Mr. Berman holds a BA degree in Economics and Accounting and a MBA in Finance from the University of Chicago.

 
                







